{"tid":1168214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣熱門話題討論區] 一齊傾下 台灣 PTT","createTime":"2019-05-23T13:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T04:32:27.000Z","uid":106212,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"df153a5ddec3f7f1d2086eb8345969ae0b8f80b3","tid":1168214,"uid":106212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:50:51.000Z","msg":"我自己有上開台灣 ptt，我知連登應該都有其他巴絲打會留意 ptt 、留意台灣嘅網絡話題<br />\n所以我喺度開個post 大家交流一下台灣嘅網絡熱門話題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除 PTT 之外，仲有例如 Disp、Dcard、爆料公社 或者其他地方見到有話題，都可以喺度 share，大家一齊討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7147f59fa503448c3cd80d5b5e3ee4e4e68db6","tid":1168214,"uid":106212,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:51:04.000Z","msg":"我拋磚先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，前一排睇到個post好搞笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜點秋香<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/joke/M.1557110571.A.5FB.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fjoke%2FM.1557110571.A.5FB.html&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=f69ed3c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/joke/M.1557110571.A.5FB.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n背景資料 :<br />\n事緣係韓國瑜競選高雄市長嘅時候已經畀人話佢政綱好空泛。最近質詢大會佢又係講埋啲「會令高雄發大財」嘅 9up 野，啲議員問佢發財方法係咩，佢就係咁重複話會令高雄發財，但就係講唔出有咩方法發財。<br />\n<br />\n答詢自經區 韓國瑜跳針「發大財」 議員翻白眼<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6267537/article-答詢自經區-韓國瑜跳針「發大財」-議員翻白眼/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6267537%2Farticle-%E7%AD%94%E8%A9%A2%E8%87%AA%E7%B6%93%E5%8D%80-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E8%B7%B3%E9%87%9D%E3%80%8C%E7%99%BC%E5%A4%A7%E8%B2%A1%E3%80%8D-%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E7%BF%BB%E7%99%BD%E7%9C%BC%2F&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=1858cc7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6267537/article-答詢自經區-韓國瑜跳針「發大財」-議員翻白眼/</a><br />\n<br />\n所以 PTT 網民就將「唐伯虎點秋香」出對聯個一幕改編成韓國瑜版本"},{"pid":"9d66a62774b52285937680365e3e9679b2a9643f","tid":1168214,"uid":106212,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:51:19.000Z","msg":"近日最熱門當然係同性婚姻法<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[新聞] 同婚專法過後&hellip;女同志想「借精生子」 名醫FB被灌爆：只能無奈拒絕</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1558486721.A.F92.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1558486721.A.F92.html&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=3b3977d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1558486721.A.F92.html</a><br />\n<br />\n&rarr; Joker3: 來來來 要精的都來找我 保證純用純天然方法進行<br />\n&rarr; kinki999: 套一句這是人權啊啊啊啊，又要解套了<br />\n推 zx930217: 這根本沒什麼議題好嗎==隨便找個男的都能借<br />\n&rarr; james784858: 180公分 基因優良 要借的找我<br />\n推 b19900127: 這個何必問醫生，上ptt一卡車的精子讓你取之不盡用之<br />\n噓 laliga: 健康教育沒教嗎？倒進去就有了這麼簡單。<br />\n噓 lupin2401: 代理孕母發大財"},{"pid":"a65c323200b9186b3258de7a9ab4dcbb15787add","tid":1168214,"uid":106212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:51:44.000Z","msg":"另外都好多人討論台灣新聞媒體嘅亂象，假新聞等等，香港其實都有類似亂象，各位巴打都可以討論一下香港媒體，捉啲假新聞出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[爆卦] 牛津大學台灣媒體調查</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1558513057.A.74F.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1558513057.A.74F.html&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=a1a9e687\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1558513057.A.74F.html</a>"},{"pid":"7316ab1e6f66591c26f7689de0006f596ca4a4bc","tid":1168214,"uid":73381,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:52:08.000Z","msg":"你返過去同班台狗討論啦 戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226ee891d47ecd380a9fe5fa5b125cd881188160","tid":1168214,"uid":106212,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:52:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>[問卦] 說真的，忍心看中國人吃草嗎</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1558504667.A.910.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1558504667.A.910.html&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=8b9bff2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1558504667.A.910.html</a><br />\n<br />\n推 simon860730: 草有點高級  吃屎比較快<br />\n推 lin821: 可以賣草給中國人<br />\n推 blinkin: 吃素很貴知道嗎<br />\n推 onlyone23: 不忍心中國妹子吃草 來台灣讓我好好愛<br />\n推 yaieki: 還可以吃蟲啊蛋白質豐富 有什麼好不忍心的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bJWCbuA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbJWCbuA.gif&h=94ec8e00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de006ef2b9d09724d250e6cd10b1c3127666be55","tid":1168214,"uid":106212,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:53:11.000Z","msg":"睇完呢個post，我覺得香港同台灣都面對一樣嘅問題，就係女仔只要正正常常就一定有仔溝，但男仔如果只有正常 level 的話係未必溝到女<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[討論] 為何女生找對象那麼重視錢，男生不會?</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/WomenTalk/M.1558482502.A.4CB.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FWomenTalk%2FM.1558482502.A.4CB.html&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhHGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=dc94ab64\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/WomenTalk/M.1558482502.A.4CB.html</a><br />\n<br />\n小魯發現有一個現象以前的台男再窮再苦不管何職業都娶得到老婆<br />\n現在男生即使身高和長相正常，甚至高率也很難找對象<br />\n問題卡在錢<br />\n通常女生找對象都會打聽男生做何職業，年收多少、未來有何發展<br />\n有沒有車子房子，如果台女聽了不爽就不必聯絡了，男生聯誼則不會去問女生薪水<br />\n、收入高低、有沒有車房，頂多知道女生職業，收入是否穩定而已<br />\n那我就好奇男生即使高薪錢也不見得會分給女生花啊，有錢人也有節儉的<br />\n那為何女生找對象要很重視男生的經濟條件啊，這樣問不會讓男生反感嗎<br />\n不是男女平等嗎，為何女生找對象會很重視錢，男生則不會呢<br />\n請解惑"},{"pid":"738b405f08a919a3ea0200fcbf8ddc760aae7ff5","tid":1168214,"uid":106320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:57:44.000Z","msg":"PTT好似無咩成